guildJoin.title: Thank you for using {{COM:bot.name}}!
description: To support the bot and unlock special features use `/premium` in your server.
To view the commands of this bot use `/help`.
To setup the bot run `/setup` in your server.
To set your birthday use `/set`.
View the {{COM:bot.name}} [Documentation]({{COM:links.docs}}) or [FAQ]({{COM:docLinks.faq}}).
For more support join the {{COM:bot.name}} support server [here]({{COM:links.support}})!
[Kevin Novak](https://github.com/KevinNovak) has created a handy [map time zone picker]({{COM:links.map}})!
Simply click your location on the map and copy the name of the selected time zone. You can then use it in the `/set` command.

support.description: For support join our discord server [here]({{COM:links.support}})!

permissions.title: {{COM:bot.name}} - Permissions
permissions.description: Want to restrict commands to certain roles, users, or channels? Set up permissions under the bot's **Integration** page in the Server Settings (or simply right-click the bot and select **Manage Integration**).

general.title: {{COM:bot.name}} General Help
description: {{COM:bot.name}} helps your server celebrate birthdays with automatic birthday roles and announcements.
**/premium** - See information about {{COM:bot.name}} Premium.
**/subscribe** - Subscribe to {{COM:bot.name}} Premium!
**/help {{REF:types.premium}}** - Help for {{COM:bot.name}} Premium.
**/set [date] [timeZone] [user]** - Set your birthday.
**/view [type] [user]** - View your information or a user's information.
**/next [type]**** - View next birthday(s) in the server.
**/list [type] [page]**** - View the server birthday list.
**/map** - View the time zone map.
**/vote** - Vote for {{COM:bot.name}}!
**/link** - View import links like faq, support, docs, etc.
**/purge** - Remove your birthday data.
**/help [type]** - Help for specific systems.
**/premium** - See information about {{COM:bot.name}} Premium.
**/settings [type]**** - View server's settings.
**/test <type> [user] [anniversary year]**** - Test the birthday event.
**/donate** - Support developments by donating!
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} General Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

blacklist.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Blacklist Help - Guild Only
description: **/blacklist add <user/role>** - Add user/role to the blacklist.
**/blacklist remove role_or_user <user/role>** - Remove a user/role from the blacklist.
**/blacklist remove id <id>** - Remove an id from the blacklist.
**/blacklist clear** - Clear the birthday blacklist.
**/blacklist list [page]** - View all blacklisted users/roles in your server.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} Blacklist Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

config.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Config Help - Guild Only
description: The [reset] option for all commands resets that setting to it's default value.
**/setup** - Interactive guide for the basic server setup.
**/config nameFormat [reset]** - Decide how {{COM:bot.name}} displays names.
**/config timeZone [reset]** - Set the default timezone for your server.
**/config useTimezone [reset]** - Decide if the bot uses the server's or user's timezone for celebrating birthdays.
**/config dateFormat [reset]** - Decide the format {{COM:bot.name}} detects dates.
**/config trustedPreventsMessage [reset]** - Decide if the trusted role should prevent the birthday message.
**/config trustedPreventsRole [reset]** - Decide if the trusted role should prevent the birthday role.
**/config requireAllTrustedRoles [reset]** - Decided if a user need all of the trusted roles.
**/config channel [reset]** - Configure the channels {{COM:bot.name}} will use.
**/config role [reset]** - Configure the birthday role.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} Config Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

message.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Message Help - Guild Only
description: **/message list <type> [page]** - List all messages for that type.
**/message add <type> <message>** - Add a message for that type.
- Example Usage: `/message add type:memberAnniversary message:<Users> have been in <Server> for <Year>(s)!`
- Placeholder for users: `{{REF:placeHolders.users}}`
- Placeholder for year: `{{REF:placeHolders.year}}` (Anniversaries only)
- Placeholder for server name: `{{REF:placeHolders.server}}`
- Placeholder for a user specific message: `@User` (Premium only)
**/message remove <type> <position>** - Remove a certain message for that type.
**/message clear <type>** - Clear all messages for that type.
**/message setting time <type> <0-23>** - Set the message time for that type
**/message setting mention <type> <role/group>** - Set the message mention setting for that type.
**/message edit embed <type> <position> <T/F>** - Update a message's embed setting.
**/message edit color <type> <position> <color/hex>** - Update a message's color setting.
**/message {{REF:types.test}} <type> <position> [user count]** - Test a custom message.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} Message Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

trusted.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Trusted System Help - Guild Only
description: **/setup {{REF:types.trusted}}** - Interactive guide for trusted system settings setup.
**/trustedRole add <role>** - Add a trusted role.
**/trustedRole remove role <role>** - Remove a trusted role.
**/trustedRole remove id <id>** - Remove a trusted role by id.
**/trustedRole clear** - Clear all trusted roles.
**/trustedRole list [page]** - List all trusted roles
**/config {{REF:types.requireAllTrustedRoles}} <T/F>** - If a user should need all the trusted roles.
**/config {{REF:types.trustedPreventsMessage}} <T/F>** - If trusted role is required for a birthday message.
**/config {{REF:types.trustedPreventsRole}} <T/F>** - If trusted role is required to get the birthday role.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} Trusted System Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

mar.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Member Anniversary Role Help - Guild Only
description: **/memberAnniversaryRole add <year> <role>** - Add a member anniversary role.
**/memberAnniversaryRole remove <year>** - Remove the member anniversary role of the given year.
**/memberAnniversaryRole clear** - Clear all member anniversary roles.
**/memberAnniversaryRole list [page]** - List all member anniversary roles.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).

footer.text: {{COM:bot.name}} Member Anniversary Role Help ● Join the support server for assistance.

premium.title: {{COM:bot.name}} Premium Help - Guild Only
description: **/premium** - View information about your server's premium.
**/message {{REF:types.add}} <type> <message>** - Add a user specific message for that type.
- Example Usage: `/message add type:birthday message:Happy Birthday @Stqlth!`
- Placeholder for year: `{{REF:placeHolders.year}}`
- Placeholder for server name: `{{REF:placeHolders.server}}`
**/message edit color <type> <position> <color/hex>** - Update a message's color setting.
**/message list userSpecificBirthday [page]** - List all user-specific birthday messages.
**/message list userSpecificMemberAnniversary [page]** - List all user-specific member anniversary messages.
**/memberAnniversaryRole add <year> <role>** - Add a member anniversary role.
**/memberAnniversaryRole remove <year>** - Remove the member anniversary role of the given year.
**/memberAnniversaryRole clear** - Clear all member anniversary roles.
**/memberAnniversaryRole list [page]** - List all member anniversary roles.
If you have any question/problems please join our support server [here]({{COM:links.support}}).
